Description:
We are looking for Senior Product manager, who will working with analytics, engineering and business teams on building marketplace algorithms, leading the team, coordinating with stakeholders, driving discovery and delivery.




Responsibilities

Leading the product team;
Working closely with engineers, data scientists and analysts;
Defining priorities and strategy, scoping projects, eliminating blockers.




Qualifications

3+ years of experience as a product manager in technical / data-science focused products (pricing/auctions, advertising systems / anti-fraud, etc.;)
Experience in product creation and development;
Willingness to work independently and solve problems;
Good communication skills;
English language proficiency at the B2 or C1+ level;
Technical background would be a plus.




Conditions & Benefits

Stable salary, official employment;
Health insurance;
Hybrid work mode and flexile schedule;
Relocation package offered for candidates from other regions;
Access to professional counseling services including psychological, financial, and legal support;
Discount club membership;
Diverse internal training programs;
Partially or fully payed additional training courses;
All necessary work equipment.

